No one needs PayPal in Ghana except fraud boys … 
@samgeorgegh
 wake up and do what Ghanaians were voted for … ban of porn , anti LGBTQ bill, reduction in data prices and the ban of Galamsey.. that’s what we asked for … not PayPal so internet fraud which is already high will go

Galamsey hurts everyone - even those who partake in it - be it in the pits or at the GoldBod, where they receive their riches from selling blood gold!
