@JDMahama
 isn’t arresting Wuntumi because of the offensive comments he made about him. But because he is the center of galamsey whose operations damaged our water bodies accross the country.

#Ghana  On #WorldEnvironmentDay, 
@TheMFWA
, 
@arochaghana
, UniMAC-IJ, and GJA convened a “seminar of conscience” spotlighting how environmental journalism holds polluters to account - from #Galamsey to plastic waste. https://ow.ly/6WRr50W8yzJ

Please don’t skip thisUse the next five minutes to listen to the commitment of the Minister of Lands and Natural Resources (
@mlnrgovgh
), the Honourable Emmanuel Armah-Kofi Buah (
@ArmahKofiBuah
), in addressing galamsey. The fight will be won .

This week Merton & Everett LLP (
@MertonEverett
) with the support of Pro Bono Legal Impact Fund-PBLIF  will be filing a lawsuit  on behalf of Democracy Hub (
@Ghfixthecountry
)

The suit will challenge the GoG's decision to deport rather prosecute the Chinese caught in Galamsey.
